	r rooted in duality\; not just sonically\, but also emotionally. Together\
	, they create a space that feels both intimate and expansive\, where softn
	ess\, healing\, and self-expression take center stage.Framed as a space to
	 unmask and reconnect\, the tour leans into themes of vulnerability and th
	e divine feminine\, inviting audiences to tap into a more instinctive and 
